description:
I had a dream where I was sitting by a lake next to a mountain, an angel called down to me saying “how can you breathe down there?” I looked up and realized I was actually underwater I swam up to the surface and there was a celebration going on. I emerged from the waters into what I think was heaven and the gathering in honor of my arrival.
-i’ve had dreams that have turned into déjà vus, i’m hoping this was one of them.
